response.overview: Featuring some of the hottest names in reggae and dancehall music, this live concert celebration is a treat for fans of sizzling island rhythms and irresistible beats. With artists including Junior Tucker, Baby Wayne, Leroy Smart, Jack Raddics, Professor Nuts and Chaka Demus & Pliers, this is one show not to be missed.
response.title: Reggae Salute
